272
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:41,080
Nema vise poseta!

273
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:45,400
- sta?
- Samo reci "da".

274
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:51,120
Ovo je novi pocetak.

275
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:58,880
Znas, imam osecaj da
cemo se lepo slagati.

276
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:03,040
Kupatilo, kuhinja...

277
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:06,600
I tvoja soba...

278
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:11,520
Dopada ti se?

279
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:22,600
- zivis sama?
- Samo ja.

280
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:25,200
Nas dve.

281
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:32,999
- sta je ovo?
- caj od kamilice.

282
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:35,360
Pomoci ce ti da zaspis.

283
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:41,839
Znas, ako budes imala nocne more,

284
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:45,520
ucinicu sve da nestanu, bas sve.

285
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:47,600
Vec jesi.

286
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,840
Laku noc!

287
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,999
- Stigli smo.
- Hvala!

288
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:44,399
Samo cu da pokupim nekoliko stvari.

289
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:47,799
- Evo kljuc!
- Vi necete da uðete?

290
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:50,399
