417
00:42:21,480 --> 00:42:23,560
Ko te je zvao?

418
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:26,240
Da li je to bila Lily?

419
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:32,560
Da li ti je nesto rekla?
Nesto sto te je uplasilo?

420
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:37,000
- El Tiho...
- El Tiho?

421
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:40,320
sta to znaci?

422
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:45,600
- Hombre.
- To je covek?

423
00:43:20,480 --> 00:43:21,959
